Nigerian artiste, Portable, has begged his fellow entertainer, Wizkid, to help up-and-coming artistes. He made this known in an interview with Time Agbaje on Tuesday. “Abeg, make una help me, I still need help. U dey hear? Make una help me abeg. Wizkid, you know Wizkid? Baba nla, Make them help. You no understand, no be to dey post motor o, no be to dey post house o, make them help people for trenches. All those artistes dey wey be say them sabi”, he said. ALSO READ: Actress Funke Akindele loses mum Meanwhile, he revealed that Davido promised to give him one song. “Because he promised to give me one song, one verse make I use am blow,” Portable added. 